175
00:12:00,595 --> 00:12:03,264
Woo Dae-sung!

176
00:12:11,314 --> 00:12:12,357
Chocolate milk skin!

177
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:15,068
-Woo Dae-sung!
-Woo Dae-sung!

178
00:12:29,207 --> 00:12:30,959
Just a bit faster.

179
