2ND: WOO DAE-SUNG

180
00:12:51,562 --> 00:12:52,730
<i>Woo Dae-sung,</i>

181
00:12:52,814 --> 00:12:54,649
you've always placed first.

182
00:12:54,983 --> 00:12:58,611
How do you feel about missing the gold
and winning the silver medal?

183
00:13:01,906 --> 00:13:04,409
-I'm sorry.
-Dae-sung, good job!

184
00:13:05,201 --> 00:13:07,078
You're the best!

185
00:13:07,161 --> 00:13:08,579
You did awesome!

186
00:13:13,209 --> 00:13:14,168
You're hot!

187
00:13:20,091 --> 00:13:22,719
Second place is still great.

188
00:13:48,786 --> 00:13:52,081
Don't you want to be a national athlete?
Why haven't you stayed in shape?

189
00:13:52,790 --> 00:13:54,959
And you said
you're happy with second place?

190
00:14:09,057 --> 00:14:09,891
<i>Heon.</i>

191
00:14:10,516 --> 00:14:14,479
<i>Geon isn't well.</i>
<i>I don't think we can make it to Korea.</i>

192
00:14:15,271 --> 00:14:17,565
<i>Can you hold the memorial service</i>
<i>on your own?</i>

193
00:14:18,149 --> 00:14:20,651
<i>I'll come to Korea next month</i>
<i>no matter what.</i>

194
00:14:29,994 --> 00:14:31,579
Dae-sung, great work.

195
00:14:31,746 --> 00:14:33,289
Jin-hwan and Ha-young left

196
00:14:33,456 --> 00:14:36,334
because they had to go to the academy
and a family dinner.

197
00:14:36,417 --> 00:14:38,836
It's okay. You're here, Brother.

198
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:40,380
Thanks a lot for coming.

199
00:14:40,463 --> 00:14:42,382
Don't mention it. We're friends.

200
00:14:43,007 --> 00:14:45,134
I'll buy you dinner today.

201
00:14:45,218 --> 00:14:47,053
What do you think about pork belly?

202
00:14:47,637 --> 00:14:50,473
I'm sorry. I'd love to have pork belly,

203
00:14:50,556 --> 00:14:51,766
but I have something to do.

204
00:14:52,725 --> 00:14:53,559
Wait.

205
00:14:54,769 --> 00:14:56,646
HOW IS IT GOING? I'LL BE THERE SOON!

206
00:14:58,189 --> 00:14:59,816
I have to go now.

207
00:14:59,899 --> 00:15:02,944
That's too bad. We can catch up next time.

208
00:15:03,027 --> 00:15:04,862
Let's have pork belly when I place first.

209
00:15:04,946 --> 00:15:07,448
Sorry. I have something
really important to do today.

210
00:15:08,199 --> 00:15:10,493
Second place is super great, too.

211
00:15:10,576 --> 00:15:12,829
I don't know why
people only care about the first place.

212
00:15:12,912 --> 00:15:13,830
Thanks.

213
00:15:15,289 --> 00:15:17,417
