216
00:15:21,504 --> 00:15:22,964
I'll make it properly next time.

217
00:15:23,047 --> 00:15:24,215
I like Dae-sang better.

218
00:15:25,049 --> 00:15:27,510
If you give me that, I'll give you this.

219
00:15:28,136 --> 00:15:31,055
Gosh! No, thanks. That's too precious.

220
00:15:37,437 --> 00:15:40,106
I'll upgrade that to a gold medal
when I win one.

221
00:15:40,356 --> 00:15:41,315
All right?

222
00:15:44,527 --> 00:15:46,571
<i>I'm fine. Don't worry.</i>

223
00:15:49,532 --> 00:15:51,659
Okay. I'll get going.

224
00:15:51,742 --> 00:15:53,703
-Okay.
-Sorry. See you in school.

225
